{"tid":853344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪基亞不太願意和曼聯續約","createTime":"2018-10-08T13:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T02:18:54.000Z","uid":124292,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"cf838913ee64c3c13055d32468f3f9d751e13c06","tid":853344,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:51:21.000Z","msg":"根據《每日電訊報》記者James Ducker報道，迪基亞不太願意再和曼聯續約。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯正在激活迪基亞合約上的優先延期一年選項，這樣他的合約就會在下賽季末到期。但雙方關於續約的談判目前陷入了停滯，現在曼聯面臨著越來越大的威脅&mdash;&mdash;可能他們會在2020年失去屆時成為自由球員的迪基亞，或者被迫在那之前就將迪基亞出售。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯現在還有時間來勸說迪基亞長期留隊。但迪基亞下個月就將滿28歲，他希望能為頂級的國內榮譽和歐戰榮譽去奮鬥，但曼聯目前的掙扎情況也引起了迪基亞的疑慮，他懷疑他們是否能在這兩條戰線上發起挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n目前，主帥摩連奴的未來也是游移不定，因此迪基亞不想在球會充滿不確定性的這段時間決定他的未來。<br />\n<br />\n上週五，曼聯方面的官員和迪基亞的經紀人門迪斯在倫敦見了面，但他們沒能就續約達成一致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2018/10/08/david-de-gea-reluctant-commit-beyond-current-deal-asmanchester/?WT.mc_id=tmg_share_em\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2Fdavid-de-gea-reluctant-commit-beyond-current-deal-asmanchester%2F%3FWT.mc_id%3Dtmg_share_em&d=4M1Ay0u2QmYh%2BS6rfY5nGp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=2af9ebe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2018/10/08/david-de-gea-reluctant-commit-beyond-current-deal-asmanchester/?WT.mc_id=tmg_share_em</a>"},{"pid":"e221422d162e3e0ba268044c93f5a7dea8b5ccff","tid":853344,"uid":54025,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:02:03.000Z","msg":"去得邊。<br />\n<br />\n皇疤拜唔洗龍門<br />\n<br />\n都係得返留隊同psg揀"},{"pid":"e5a6d30deea203e42cda87d522915e1713ba6736","tid":853344,"uid":158613,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"星散"},{"pid":"d7eaf0c045c0e177338dce17b900080e36f51365","tid":853344,"uid":130419,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"佢走應該去 巴黎 祖記 是但一隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla